Parent Portal 




The Parent Portal allows a student's parent or legal guardian access to his/her grades and attendance. In order to use this tool, you must receive a letter from Amherst ISD with a Portal ID code. Once you have received this letter, you will need to follow the directions (which you can access in the Attachment below which opens in Microsoft Word) to set up your account. Please note that Amherst ISD is not capable of retrieving lost logins, or passwords so it is imperative that you keep this information in a safe place. 

Check Student grades here. 


